  "description": "OBRIX's harmonic field controls when drum hits are allowed through. Loud OBRIX sections choke the percussion; quiet sections let drums breathe. A call-and-response between the living reef and the surface splash — tonal and percussive elements compete for space like organisms in a shared ecosystem.",
